review: We got dental braces set for my daughter to get her uneven teeth set right. We were referred to Dr. Kishore from other doctor and were fortunate to get the treatment done at his clinic. Dr. Kishore is very professional and diligent. He and his team are very organised and courteous, which makes your every visit pleasant and comfortable. I am sure it will be the same experience whoever visit his clinic. I definitely recommend Dr. Kishore for his experience, skills and right treatment for any dental procedure, be assured you are at the right place. Thank you doctor.

review: The Dr is very versed in his field and takes every effort to explain the existing condition and the treatment required, the cost, time duration of treatment, precautions, follow-up details etc right before the beginning of the great. This in turn gives us confidence and clarity to take the treatment, considering dental procedures are time taking over long periods of time. The ambience of the facility and staff are very friendly. They take all precautions for hygiene and safety as well.
